Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做到了  丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还讨厌竞赛会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在刚才  我喜欢上它了
